    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required level 2. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 1 against required level 2 due to single test condition; this shortfall is accepted given the strong quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and the conservative nature of ASTM F1717 as a standardized worst-case loading protocol. Overall credibility sufficient for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence COU.",
